# HighAsCG — paths omitted from the live USB squashfs (penguins-eggs / mksquashfs)
#
# mksquashfs is invoked with -wildcards; entries are relative to the image root
# (no leading slash), anchored at the top of the filesystem.
# Using "/*" omits *contents*; the parent directory (empty) is still in the image.
# See: work/docs/LIVE_USB_IMAGE.md §4.2.1
#
home/serwer/*
opt/casparcg/media/*
